Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多想确认的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是拇指姑娘的故事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我 是演什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想扮演什么角色？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以自己决定么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就跟你决定自己的活法是一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这个故事没有角色分配的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这个故事里 本来就没有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你得自己来想来决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连那种准备都没做好就闯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪想得到会出这档子事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底我都不知道自己会把身体借出去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你还为什么要挺身来这里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…一时冲动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连能不能回去也不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好办了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事也是有可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回不去我会怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直保持这种状态会不会很糟糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定自己的角色么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 我基本上是个乐观主义者所以也没啥大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就很介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 真没真没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗话说有始必有终啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有不会停的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要人还活着雨就总会停的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是要看店长的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你稀里糊涂的就真会迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就回不去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的是店长的丈夫才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没动摇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想让店长转向我这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让她笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 要脱多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部脱光？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都没计划性的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 只要后背就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下半身就这样直接去泡澡么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变得湿漉漉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明也知道我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还能张得了口让我做这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 把这件事忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把衣服穿上 拒绝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才拒绝得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会先进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之后过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要跟我一起洗么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定 小六花也挺愿意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在某时某地跟叶月君进展不顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她心里也还是会无意识地期待这种事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是什么坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后背变的好柔软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这么白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不炼出点肌肉来可不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啊 后背很脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能脏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有动物的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢抚摸你的后背
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这活着的声音从你身后传过来 毫无防备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人安心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你 不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经把新的后背…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡 还是做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉拌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我消失了的话事情就简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是想在你身边多呆一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是一点没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然变心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都喜欢上了 就得承认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:54.96,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月…君…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然总有一天会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算多么不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:06:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果王子不回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 难道那样的话就只有我一个人出局么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能允许这种悲剧发生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是王子的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 之前好不容易才把店长带到游乐园去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才刚刚开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是纯真无邪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是个老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了岛尾君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么那么喜欢店长呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我为什么我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么为她着想到这种程度呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢她什么地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契机呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契机？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:08:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始 我只是觉得这个初中男生背挺得真直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 说实话是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊 发生了点事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看的话就偶然发现她浇水时手边出现了彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她沉浸在那道光里的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得她真像个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是视线就没法从她身上移开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对她的第一印象是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可稍微了解一下的话就觉得她也很有大人样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又很有店长的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走过她身边总能闻到土壤的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都让我觉得…只是觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然 很喜欢她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:08:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拇指公主接下来就HE了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被青蛙掳走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被金龟子抢去当新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被老鼠婆婆照顾什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是燕子的翅膀痊愈之后还是会去花田里见王子么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子的脑子秀逗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想完成这个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就 赶紧回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我先引诱你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.52,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得对不起我么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你结果还是在想着顺其自然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始这就只是时间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心拒绝什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一次都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再这样用死去的丈夫做挡箭牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月君…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛尾君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…要怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是转移下注意力比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要写什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:05.08,setting,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz18.809\pos(157,130)}今 天 的 推 荐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推荐什么的 我还真是不擅长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先把价格适中的花按颜色和大小分好类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后让客人从中自由选择主花材再做成花束就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不难吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是勉强去跟人推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而还会让对方觉得你不擅长到时候起反效果哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是这么说 不过总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是不讨厌向客人推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照当天的天气和心情适当地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那些不知道选择什么花的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供一个契机就好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花你太正经了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然察言观色也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能太过于纠结别人的脸色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花你不来做决定的话客人也会困扰的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用那么拐弯抹角的说法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾想过帮叶月修剪头发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 只是想摸摸他的后背
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得自己决定自己到底想怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困扰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…灯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是忘了关了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷藏柜OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柜台…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 我忘了关抽屉么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近做事还真是马虎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊 这幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主镇守着沉淀的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盆栽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防腐剂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不管怎么拔还是不见少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊小六花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天一大早就找你过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一角完事了之后就休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越有夏天的感觉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想趁着凉快的时候赶快完事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊都是我拉着你给店里帮忙耽误了时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是自己嫌麻烦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可放着不管的话它们又会一顿疯长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美惠姐你家有院子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这院子小得可怜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够宽敞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 我做了紫苏汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自制的 很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少放糖 多放柠檬酸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都长得比我还高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过几天 我想在这里种上蔷薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 长长的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就像爱丽丝梦游仙境里的迷宫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛尾君你的少女兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女情结让人起鸡皮疙瘩 我挺喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么让人起鸡皮疙瘩你这是人身攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这想法本来就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是命薄如纸也要恋爱的少女？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种装脆弱的行为才让人受不了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是装呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是单纯地很喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倩女命薄亦逢恋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一腔热血尚暖时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何惧明朝日月浅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛尾君修剪造型很勤快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很擅长栽培大朵的蔷薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这阵子 花数多了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这种小朵的蔷薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是我喜欢的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花朵有时候太能说会道也让人伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有主人的夏天的院子就更是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作很忙么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说忙也没什么 我反正只要在家工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明也有工作要做的 一直让你帮忙真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去店里正好能解决我运动不足 正合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能这么说真让我安心不少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花你是不是工作上太努力了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有休息么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就相当于休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这不就只是来让我差遣的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有其他的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正工作也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我独身没资格说这话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不适合做寡妇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花你一个人揽了太多事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说啊 老顾客中有没有年轻的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了突然间？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天附近的图书馆下午1点就要关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的时候正好去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得收拾下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事就那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我下次再来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉各种被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 说我不适合做寡妇什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能让我来选蔷薇呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛尾君种的蔷薇 漂亮的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是没有死心么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使说我必须往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算在你心里一辈子都第二也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心拒绝什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一次都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明也知道我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还能张得了口让我做这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢我么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 比如说和我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈次婚外恋怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会比店长您活得更长哦 虽然有点对不住您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就算您说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会退缩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不转过头来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就大喊大叫了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次休假的时候能去么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:30.01,SETTING2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz12.592\pos(126,62)}入园招待券
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:30.01,SETTING3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz12.095\pos(160,113)}1张仅限一位使用（4岁以下儿童免费）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:30.01,setting,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz12.029\pos(187,150)}有效期限不限  非卖品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从宣传的人那里拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再这样用死去的丈夫做挡箭牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我让他背过身去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听一个年纪比我小的人说了些好听的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就有点轻飘飘的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得反正他还年轻经得起折腾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人鱼公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就伤害了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都干了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟个笨蛋似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆内禁止私语
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月君？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆内请不要大声喧哗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 那个很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个量的确会让人以为你是要搞暑假自由研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 只和我先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只和我先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先生…是我的初恋…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说真正谈过恋爱的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有岛尾君一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说和岛尾君那时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来也是我先单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以到了这种年纪还会有人喜欢上我什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也从来没想过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没想过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢叶月君你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:31.99,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつも夢の中では あなたは笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:31.99,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦中的你永远是笑着的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:39.73,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうして ねえ 消えないの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:39.73,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何不曾消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给了你一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:43.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me anything？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:43.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给了我什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:46.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっといつまででも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:46.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是永恒不变的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.35,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.35,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.14,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still my everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:53.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛してるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:53.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:59.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夏に降った 雪のような
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:59.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正如盛夏里飘落的雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:05.42,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは儚い奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:05.42,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个易碎的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:07.06,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かまわない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:07.06,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:12.73,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたに出会わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:12.73,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是没有遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:19.59,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こんなに切なくて 胸を締め付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:19.59,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也不会如此绞痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:23.51,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こともなかったそれでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:23.51,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.51,0:22:29.20,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたに出会えなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.51,0:22:29.20,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是没能遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:36.06,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強さも優しさも 知らずにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:36.06,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就无法领悟强大与温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:45.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目を閉じればすぐそこに あなたがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:45.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼你就在离我那么近的地方
